<section>

<div class="hero">

<h1 class="my0">
  Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Odit, illo ad.
</h1>

<div class="sub-h1 my0">
  Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Iure vel soluta velit? Neque perferendis asperiores perspiciatis labore? Ipsa, iure nobis.
